      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大吹打〗。四龙套、四上手引马芳同上。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00002",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "马芳"
      ],
      "text": "执掌兵权，威风八面，雄兵万，扫灭狠烟，扶保锦江山。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00003",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马芳上台。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00004",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "马芳"
      ],
      "text": "威风凛凛坐将台，兵机战策满胸怀。龙虎二将来保驾，扶保大明九龙台。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00005",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马芳"
      ],
      "text": "本帅，姓马名芳，字文成。大明驾前为臣，令奉圣命，带领人马，镇守榆林关一带。今当三、六、九日操演之期。众将官，兵发校场听点！",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00006",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "唢呐二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "马芳"
      ],
      "text": "有马芳坐将台忙传将令，叫一声众儿郎细听分明：太平年吃粮饷安然自在，离乱年一个个就要出征。上前者得胜回有功有赏，退后者一定要插耳游营。帅字旗不住在空中飘映，且听探马报军情。",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00007",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "探子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00008",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "探子"
      ],
      "text": "打探军情事。报与元帅知。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00009",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "探子"
      ],
      "text": "报：探子告进。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01013005_e00010",
      "play_id": "01013005",
      "scene_id": "01013005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马芳"
      ],
      "text": "打探得哪路军情，一一道来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
